data.description: Beautiful 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms ,NEWLY REMODELED ,home nestled in the heart of Glendale. Beautiful floor plan, as you enter you will see a spacious living room, with a family room to the left that's open to the totally remodeled new kitchen and separate dinning room. Tile Throughout and freshly painted. Home is adjacent to Country Gables Park, close to Arrowhead Mall, shopping, freeways and Universities. ,. The large backyard with great awning for shade has RV gate and parking on one side and slab for storage shed on the other.NO HOA.
